data.description: Priced UNDER appraised value! Welcome to 414 South Ave, a hidden gem with incredible potential. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home presents an exciting canvas for investors, builders, or those with a keen eye for transformation. With an effective year built in 1965, this property offers a unique chance to create something truly special.**Property Highlights:**- 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms- Spacious layout with ample potential- Unleash your creativity and bring your vision to life- Conveniently located only 10 minutes from Eglin Air Force Base- A short 20-minute drive to Hurlburt Field414 South Ave provides the perfect foundation to make your real estate dreams a reality. Bring your offers and let your imagination run wild. Contact us today to schedule a viewing.
